### PANAPAGOS - Test Payment Flow

### 1. Crear Link de Pago
POST http://localhost:4000/v1/checkout/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "merchantId": "clzxxx",
  "amount": 150000,
  "currency": "PYG",
  "description": "Compra de producto premium",
  "expirationSeconds": 3600
}

### 2. Obtener detalles del link (reemplazar {shortCode} con el código generado)
GET http://localhost:4000/v1/checkout/link/{shortCode}

### 3. Procesar pago
POST http://localhost:4000/v1/checkout/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "transaction-id-here",
  "cardNumber": "4111111111111111",
  "cardHolder": "JUAN PEREZ",
  "expiryDate": "12/25",
  "cvv": "123",
  "documentType": "CI",
  "documentNumber": "1234567",
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.1",
  "userAgent": "Mozilla/5.0"
}

### 4. Consultar estado de transacción
GET http://localhost:4000/v1/checkout/transaction/{transactionId}
